column5: ~~~~Brother of mine lives in Kentucky, and we got together this summer, at a buddy's cottage for a week with plans to do nothing but drink eat and phishe not in that order. So next year we could improve on it, so I'm a thunken of headen down to Tenn. to this sweet looken Resort http://www.bluebankresort.com/
